						               													<description>Strategy game with resource management mechanics for 2-4 players in which players fight to become the new king of the island using their army of slimes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A long, long time ago, some little creatures began to populate this island. Over time, they formed a society divided into groups according to their specialty and ruled by a king. A long, long time has passed since these days, but if you look carefully through the dense forests, over the high mountains and across the green meadows, you will find slimes who have made this island their home.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Now, the slime king is dead! An era of power struggle has begun. You, the leader of a village of slimes, want to be the new king but you are not the only one. As written in the slime law, you will fight from next spring to next winter to increase your army and strengthen your power. At the end of the year, whoever has the largest army will rule the island. Will you be the new king of slimes? Prove yourself in the fight for the crown!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
